# UI Components

The application uses Bootstrap 5 with custom styling for its interface. Key UI components include:

## Score Display
- **Score Container**: Displays the numerical score with percentage
- **Progress Bars**: Gradient-colored bars showing score levels
- **Score Classes**: Uses 'success', 'warning', and 'danger' classes to indicate quality

## Content Editor
- **Quill Editor**: Rich text editor for content management
- **Character Counters**: Real-time character counters for title and meta description

## Feedback Components
- **List Groups**: Used to display SEO feedback items
- **Icon System**: Uses Bootstrap Icons (bi-*) to visually indicate feedback quality

## AI Integration
- AI suggestion buttons for generating titles and meta descriptions
- Loading indicators during API calls
